<component><class>org.concord.modeler.PageTextBox</class>
<width>370.0</width>
<height>330.0</height>
<title>&lt;html&gt;
  &lt;head&gt;
    
  &lt;/head&gt;
  &lt;body face=&quot;verdana&quot;&gt;
    &lt;p style=&quot;margin-top: 0&quot;&gt;
      Your challenge is to design an electric field in which an electron will 
      move in an approximately straight line rather than a curved path, no 
      matter where you place the electron in the container.
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
      You can place as many positive and negative charges as you like, but can 
      only place one electron using the &lt;img height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; src=&quot;addElectronUP.png&quot;&gt; 
      button. Test your field by dropping an electron into the model to see if 
      it moves in an approximately straight line. After you have succeeded, 
      take a snapshot of your field.
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
      &lt;b&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;Note: To see how an electron moves again, press &lt;img height=&quot;16&quot; src=&quot;addElectronUP.png&quot; width=&quot;16&quot;&gt; 
      and click inside the window to add a new electron again. Press the 
      &amp;quot;Clear&amp;quot; button only when you want to redesign the field.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt; 
      &lt;/font&gt;
    &lt;/p&gt;
    &lt;p&gt;
      &lt;b&gt;&lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; name=&quot;button1&quot; alt=&quot;Hint 1&quot; script=&quot;script:page:0:message &lt;t&gt;&lt;font face=verdana&gt;You will need an array of positive charges and another array of negative charges&lt;br&gt;on each side of the container to complete this task.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/t&gt;;&quot; uid=&quot;hint1&quot; value=&quot;Hint #1&quot;&gt;
      &lt;input type=&quot;submit&quot; name=&quot;button2&quot; alt=&quot;Hint 2&quot; script=&quot;script:page:0:message &lt;t&gt;&lt;font face=verdana&gt;Try to create a field so that much of the middle of the container has field vectors&lt;br&gt;all pointing in the same direction.&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/t&gt;;&quot; uid=&quot;hint2&quot; value=&quot;Hint #2&quot;&gt;
&lt;/b&gt;    &lt;/p&gt;
  &lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;
</title>
